                <h3>Dabeli</h3>
                <p>Dabeli is a popular Indian street food originating from the Kutch region of Gujarat. It's a spicy and tangy snack made by stuffing a bun with a spiced potato mixture, topped with chutneys, onions, and sev.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;100</p>
                <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span>  
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="imagesguju/starters/dhokla.jpg" alt="dhokla">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Dhokla</h3>
                <p>Dhokla is a savory steamed cake made from fermented rice and chickpea flour batter, flavored with spices like mustard seeds, curry leaves, and green chilies.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;60</p>
                 <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span> 
            </div>
