            <img src="imagesguju/starters/fafda.jpg" alt="fafda">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Fafda</h3>
                <p>Fafda is a crunchy and savory snack from the state of Gujarat, made from gram flour (besan) dough, rolled into thin strips, and deep-fried until golden brown.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;120</p>
                 <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span> 
            </div>
        </div>
