            <img src="imagesguju/starters/khandvi.jpg" alt="khandvi">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Khandvi</h3>
                <p>Khandvi is a savory snack from Gujarat made from gram flour (besan) and yogurt batter cooked into thin, silky rolls, tempered with mustard seeds and coconut.
</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;40</p>
                 <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span> 
            </div>
        </div>
