                <p>Patra, also known as Alu Vadi, is a traditional Gujarati snack made from colocasia leaves rolled with a spiced chickpea flour mixture, steamed, and then sliced and tempered with mustard seeds and sesame seeds.</p>
                <p>Price: &#8377;150</p>
                <span style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">Veg</span>  
